  "storyTitle": "Our Story",
  "storyText": "Incial began with a simple vision: to empower brands, businesses, and ideas with innovative digital solutions that create lasting impact. Founded in 2024 in Kanjirappally, Kerala, we started as a small team of passionate creators and strategists determined to make a difference. From those first projects to now serving businesses across industries, our journey has been fueled by creativity, collaboration, and a relentless drive to push boundaries.",
